reviewText: From the title "Welding Techniques of the Pros" I assumed that I would see a general welding video.  Instead I saw how to weld aluminum which is a specialized area of welding.  Nowhere in the description or  title did it even mention aluminum.  On the other hand the video did a good  job of explaining the basic proceedures of welding aluminum and if that was  what I was looking for I would have been pleased, but I was looking for  general welding techniques and was very disapointed.
